  "detailed_description": "Simplistic top-down shooter that will put a smile on your face.<br><br>You were an ordinary citizen in a small town… Now it’s on fire! <br>Rioters are storming the houses while aliens rampage in the sky! <br>Run as fast as you can! Shoot anything that moves! Do not release the gas pedal!<br>Anarchy has never been so much fun!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grab your gun and join the fun!</strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576130/extras/82739b1a761c7d9b5b18e0b7008f05d2.poster.avif?t=1742644028\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576130/extras/82739b1a761c7d9b5b18e0b7008f05d2.webm?t=1742644028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576130/extras/82739b1a761c7d9b5b18e0b7008f05d2.mp4?t=1742644028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Prepare for intense run & gun action!<br></li><li> Enjoy hilarious doodle graphics and mouth made sound effects!<br></li><li> Use 50+ weapons. New gun on every level!<br></li><li> Shoot 80+ enemies and bosses!<br></li><li> Drive 3 cars and 6 spaceships!<br></li><li> Obtain new talents and weapon upgrades!<br></li><li> Beat 48 stages!<br></li><li> Enjoy awesome rock music!</li></ul>",
